---
title: HiTicket - Sequence Diagram - Ticket PATCH (Status, Comment, Assignment)
---
sequenceDiagram
    actor Staff as Agent or Admin
    participant UI as TicketDetail UI
    participant API as Express API
    participant DB as MongoDB
    participant Notif as Notification
    participant Gmail as Gmail API

    Staff->>UI: Change status, add comment, or reassign ticket
    UI->>API: PATCH /api/tickets/:id { status, comment, assignedTo, satisfaction } + JWT
    note over API: protect middleware - verify JWT and tokenVersion
    API->>DB: Ticket.findById(id)
    DB-->>API: ticket document

    note over API: Access check - admin all, agent assigned or own, user own only

    opt Status is changing
        note over API: User role can only reopen - staff can set any status
        API->>DB: ticket.history.push({ action, field, from, to, by, byName })
        API->>DB: ticket.status = newStatus
    end

    opt assignedTo is changing (staff only)
        API->>DB: ticket.history.push assignment change entry
        API->>DB: ticket.assignedTo = newAgentName
    end

    opt comment body is provided
        API->>DB: ticket.comments.push({ text, author, authorName })
    end

    opt satisfaction rating provided and not yet set
        API->>DB: ticket.satisfaction = { rating, feedback, submittedAt: now }
    end

    API->>DB: ticket.save()
    note over DB: pre save - if status=Resolved and resolvedAt not set, set resolvedAt=now
    DB-->>API: updated ticket document
    API->>DB: ticket.populate(createdBy name email)
    DB-->>API: populated ticket
    API-->>UI: 200 { ticket } - internalNotes stripped for user role
    UI-->>Staff: Update ticket view with new state

    opt Status changed
        API--)Notif: Notification.create({ user: createdBy, type: ticket_update }) async
        API--)Gmail: sendStatusChanged(ticket, owner, oldStatus, newStatus) async
    end

    opt Comment added
        API--)Notif: Notification.create({ user: createdBy, type: comment }) async
        API--)Gmail: sendCommentAdded(ticket, owner, comment) async
    end

    opt Assignment changed and assignee user exists
        API--)Notif: Notification.create({ user: assignedUser, type: assignment }) async
        API--)Gmail: sendTicketAssigned(ticket, owner, assignedTo) async
    end
